data.description: Introducing a Luxurious Oasis in the Heart of Cane Bay, Summerville! This is a premier 55+ community.   Nestled within the picturesque community of Cane Bay, this exceptional home offers the perfect blend of modern elegance and Southern charm. Downstairs you will find dual spacious Owner Suites appealing to a wide variety of living situations including people caring for an elderly parent, two friends buying a home jointly, or parents accepting that their boomerang child who is 19+ may be a permanent fixture.  Boasting a unique Santorini Loft design upstairs is a private living area previously used as a gaming/office area that could easily be converted to fit the needs of your family whether it be a bedroom or a theater room, there is a ton of flexibility. This property is a true gem for those seeking comfort and style in a prime location.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light, accentuated by 8' doors throughout the main level, which lead you to a stunning sunroom. This sun-soaked retreat is ideal for unwinding with a good book, enjoying morning coffee, or simply basking in the serene ambiance of your surroundings.  For those who appreciate outdoor living, the screened porch and 10x12 patio provide the perfect spaces to entertain guests, dine alfresco, or watch the sunset over the lush greenery that surrounds the property. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or savoring a quiet evening under the stars, this home has you covered.  The heart of this home lies in its ultra-gourmet kitchen, a culinary dream come true. Equipped with top-of-the-line appliances and a gas cooktop, this kitchen will inspire your inner chef to create delectable meals for family and friends. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the kitchen to the dining and living areas, making it a breeze to host gatherings and enjoy quality time with loved ones.  Additional features include custom blinds for privacy and light control, ensuring your comfort and convenience at all times as well as a Generac power generator system so you will never lose power during outages!  This remarkable property is more than just a house; it's a lifestyle. Located in the desirable Cane Bay community near Summerville, you'll enjoy easy access to shopping, dining, top-rated schools, and all the amenities that this thriving area has to offer.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this sanctuary your own. Experience the epitome of low-country living with a touch of luxury. Contact us today to schedule a private tour and discover why this house is the perfect place to call home.
